        <updateDate>2021-02-25T16:01:06Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Wildland Firefighter Fair Pay Act</b></p> <p>This bill exempts federal wildland firefighters in the Department of the Interior and the Department of Agriculture from certain premium pay limitations for work relating to wildfire emergencies.</p> <p>The bill applies retroactively to January 1, 2020.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
